OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome patchy rain across the
OL,6,FTrossachs and northern Perthshire this
OL,7,Fmorning.
OL,8,
OL,9,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,10,Fsome late sunshine in places. Then the
OL,11,Frest of the night will be dry with
OL,12,Fvariable amounts of cloud.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FIt will be a dry day with
OL,15,Fvariable amounts of cloud and sunny
OL,16,Fspells, best of the sunshine later on.
OL,17,FBecoming very warm, especially in the
OL,18,Feast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
